    Waspinator opens the door and lets Drillbit enter, and watches for a 
moment as Terrorsaur dose a blitz-krieg manuver on the dinobot. He then 
closes to door so he can watch what Meg's will do.

    Paralysis greets Quickstrike in the clearing. All around are Predacon 
building autoguns and other essential machines for the new base. "Good to see 
you. The Commander is in the bunker now with Tarantulas. She told me to tell 
you to contact her when you get her. I think she wants you to go into the 
bunker with them." He says.
    He then turns and yells at Grappler to quit screwing around and to get 
back to work.

    Inside the bunker, Tarantulas moves forward first. He was bigger, 
stroner, and better amred than the tiny fembot. Thus, she ordered him to go 
in first in case of a trap. The corridor with all the doors seemed long, but 
when they got the power up and running, the lights revealed it wasnt so long 
after all. Now they had to get into the rooms.
    "Tarantulas, see if you cant hack your way into the main computer core in 
the Triangle Room. Im guessing thats Opperations."
